msgid "0:診察室にはすぐに呼ばれた。もっと待たされるかと思ったけど、全然そんなことはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "0:It wasn't long at all before I was called into the exam room. I thought I'd be asked to wait longer, but that wasn't the case at all.[%p]"

msgid "100:ロビーにいたたくさんの人たちはいったいなんだったんだろう。案外、サクラだったりするのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "100:What about all those people in the lobby? Maybe they were all fakes, put there by the hospital to make it look busy.[%p]"

msgid "200:４年前とは違う診察室だった。入っていくと、懐かしい顔が僕を出迎えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "200:It was a different exam room than the one I'd been seen in four years ago, but I recognized how he welcomed me when I came in.[%p]"

msgid "300:[name]高科[line]「やあ、西條くん」[%p]"
msgstr "300:[name]高科[line]Hello, Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "400:高科先生は親しげな笑顔を浮かべると立ち上がり、僕に手を差し出してきた。握手を求められていると気付いて、慌てて握り返す。[%p]"
msgstr "400:He stood up with a friendly smile and offered me a hand. I realized he wanted a handshake, and hurriedly shook it back.[%p]"

msgid "500:[name]高科[line]「また君に会えて、嬉しいよ」[%p]"
msgstr "500:[name]高科[line]I'm happy to see you again.[%p]"

msgid "600:[name]高科[line]「いや、嬉しい、というのは変かな」[%p]"
msgstr "600:[name]高科[line]No... maybe “happy” isn't the right word.[%p]"

msgid "700:[name]高科[line]「君にしてみれば、またここに来るというのは辛いことなわけだからね」[%p]"
msgstr "700:[name]高科[line]From your perspective, I'm sure it was hard to come back.[%p]"

msgid "800:４年振りだっていうのに、先生はすごくフレンドリーだ。[linebreak]僕は少し緊張していたんだけど、一気に気が楽になった。[%p]"
msgstr "800:It had been four years, but the doctor was still really friendly. I'd been feeling a little nervous, but I quickly calmed down.[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]高科[line]「それで、今日はどうしたんだい？」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]高科[line]So, what brings you here today?[%p]"

msgid "1000:先生にイスにかけるように促され、僕は腰を落ち着けた。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:He motioned for me to sit down, and I did.[%p]"

msgid "1100:緊張が解けたせいか、僕は一気に自分に起きたこと、起きているかもしれないことを話した。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:Maybe I felt a little too at ease, because I told him everything that had happened, and everything that might have happened.[%p]"

msgid "1200:話すことに慣れていないせいか何度もつっかえたけど、先生は僕を急かすことなくずっと真剣な顔で、相づちを打ちながら聞き入ってくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:I wasn't used to talking to people, so I kept tripping over my own words. But he never pushed me. He just nodded and listened.[%p]"

msgid "1300:もちろん優愛のことや悪魔女のことも、なにもかも話した。危険かな、と思ったけど今の僕には頼れるのはこの人しかいないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Of course, I told him about Yua, and the demon girl. Everything. It occurred to me that might be dangerous, but he was the only one I could rely on right now.[%p]"

msgid "1400:[name]高科[line]「結論から先に言おうか」[%p]"
msgstr "1400:[name]高科[line]Let me start by giving you my diagnosis.[%p]"

msgid "1500:すべてを聞いてから、高科先生は少し考え込み、そう口を開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:After I finished, he thought for a while before opening his mouth.[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]高科[line]「君は正常だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]高科[line]You're completely normal.[%p]"

msgid "1700:[name]高科[line]「なんの問題もない」[%p]"
msgstr "1700:[name]高科[line]There's nothing wrong with you.[%p]"

msgid "1800:[name]拓巳[line]「ホ、ホント……ですか……？」[%p]"
msgstr "1800:[name]拓巳[line]R-Really?[%p]"

msgid "1900:[name]高科[line]「もちろん」[%p]"
msgstr "1900:[name]高科[line]Of course.[%p]"

msgid "2000:それはなによりも期待していた言葉。[%p]"
msgstr "2000:Those were the words I wanted to hear more than anything.[%p]"

msgid "2100:これを言ってもらいたいためだけに、この病院にわざわざ足を運んだんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:I'd come all the way to this hospital just to hear them.[%p]"

msgid "2200:もし“お前は異常だ”って言われたらどうしようって、ビクビクしていた。[linebreak]でも、先生に診てもらってよかった。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:I'd been terrified he was going to say there was something wrong with me, but now I was glad I'd come.[%p]"

msgid "2300:[name]高科[line]「むしろ、おかしいのはその楠さんという女性だね」[%p]"
msgstr "2300:[name]高科[line]If anything, this young Kusunoki lady is the one who has something wrong with her.[%p]"

msgid "2400:[name]高科[line]「西條くんの話だけで判断するのは難しいが、おそらくその女性は精神的な障害を患っているだろう」[%p]"
msgstr "2400:[name]高科[line]It's difficult to make a diagnosis just from what you've told me, but she's likely suffering from some kind of mental disorder.[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]高科[line]「今後、君に危険を及ぼすような行動に出る可能性がある」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]高科[line]There's a chance she may try to harm you at some point in the future.[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]高科[line]「すぐに警察に通報しよう」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]高科[line]We should call the police immediately.[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]拓巳[line]「え……」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "2800:警察……。[linebreak]確かにそれが一番安全かも。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:The police... Yeah, that might be the safest option.[%p]"

msgid "2900:優愛は異常だ。頭がおかしいんだ。もしまたストーカー行為をされたら、と考えるとゾッとする。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:There was something wrong with Yua. She was crazy. Just the thought of her coming after me again was enough to make me shiver.[%p]"

msgid "3000:[name]高科[line]「もちろん、僕も責任を持って君を保護するつもりだ」[%p]"
msgstr "3000:[name]高科[line]Of course you can count on me to keep you safe.[%p]"

msgid "3100:僕に力強い瞳を向けて、励ますように肩を叩いてくれる。さらに、名刺まで渡された。そこには先生のケータイ番号が印刷されている。[%p]"
msgstr "3100:He gazed firmly at me, gave me a friendly pat on the shoulder, and then he even gave me his business card. It had his cell phone number on it.[%p]"

msgid "3200:[name]高科[line]「なにか問題が起きたら、いつでも連絡をくれて構わないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "3200:[name]高科[line]If something happens, call me, no matter what the time.[%p]"

msgid "3300:[name]高科[line]「２４時間、いつでも君のところに飛んでいくからね」[%p]"
msgstr "3300:[name]高科[line]I'll be there for you, 24 hours a day.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]拓巳[line]「え、い、いいん、ですか……？」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]拓巳[line]R-Really?[%p]"

msgid "3500:[name]高科[line]「当たり前だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "3500:[name]高科[line]Of course.[%p]"

msgid "3600:[name]高科[line]「僕は、君の主治医なんだから」[%p]"
msgstr "3600:[name]高科[line]I'm your primary care physician.[%p]"

msgid "3700:涙が出そうになった。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:I was almost ready to cry.[%p]"

msgid "3800:この人に担当してもらってよかったって、心からそう思う。[linebreak]今どき、こんなにいい先生はなかなかいない。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:I was so happy he was my doctor. There weren't many like him these days.[%p]"

msgid "3900:[name]高科[line]「悪魔女のことについても、通報した方がよさそうだね」[%p]"
msgstr "3900:[name]高科[line]We should probably call them about that demon girl, too.[%p]"

msgid "4000:[name]高科[line]「西條くん、君の見たその女がニュージェネの真犯人で間違いないよ。これはものすごい目撃証言だ」[%p]"
msgstr "4000:[name]高科[line]The woman you saw was clearly the NewGen killer. Your testimony will be incredibly valuable.[%p]"

msgid "4100:先生は少し興奮気味だ。[linebreak]だけど声音にはそれを出さない。[linebreak]相変わらず落ち着いた話し方。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:He was getting a little excited, but he wasn't letting it show in his voice. His tone was as calm as ever.[%p]"

msgid "4200:[name]高科[line]「事件は、西條くんのおかげで解決だ」[%p]"
msgstr "4200:[name]高科[line]Thanks to you, the case is solved.[%p]"

msgid "4300:[name]高科[line]「君は渋谷のヒーローだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "4300:[name]高科[line]You're the hero of Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "4400:[name]高科[line]「僕はこの瞬間に立ち会えて、実に光栄に思う」[%p]"
msgstr "4400:[name]高科[line]I'm truly honored to have been here for this moment.[%p]"

msgid "4500:僕が……ヒーロー……？[%p]"
msgstr "4500:I was... a hero?[%p]"

msgid "4600:エンスーじゃあるまいし。[linebreak]こんな僕がヒーローだなんてあり得ないよ。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:This wasn't ESO. A person like me couldn't be a hero.[%p]"

msgid "4700:でも想像してみたら、つい顔がにやけそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "4700:But just imagining it made me grin.[%p]"

msgid "4800:渋谷の女子中学生も女子高生も女子大生もＯＬも、誰もが僕に黄色い声援を送り、僕はカリスマ的な人気を得る。[%p]"
msgstr "4800:All the middle school girls and high school girls and college girls and office ladies in Shibuya, all screaming my name. I would be a celebrity.[%p]"

msgid "4900:テレビタレントになるのもいいけど、人前に出るのはイヤだから、ベンチャー企業を起ち上げるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:I could be on TV, but I didn't like being in front of people, so I would start a venture company instead.[%p]"

msgid "5000:そしてカリスマ社長として大儲け。会社には美人秘書をたくさんはべらせてハーレム状態。当然ながら全員フラグが立ってて僕にメロメロだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:Then I'd make a ton of money as a famous CEO. I'd have a bunch of pretty girls as secretaries in my own personal harem. Of course, they'd all be totally in love with me.[%p]"

msgid "5100:家は六本木の高層マンションで、かわいいメイドさんを何人も雇う。まさに僕専用メイドカフェって感じ。もちろん、甘くて濃厚な“夜のご奉仕”も……なんつって！\u3000なんつって！[%p]"
msgstr "5100:I'd have a high-rise condo in Roppongi and lots of cute maids at my service. Like my own personal maid café! And of course, they'd be willing to “serve” me at night, too... Just kidding! Just kidding![%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]拓巳[line]「ふひ……ふひひ……まさに勝ち組……」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]拓巳[line]Fweheheh... I'm on top of the world.[%p]"

msgid "5300:ハッと我に返ると、僕はいまだにロビーのソファに座っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:Suddenly, I realized I was still sitting on the sofa in the lobby.[%p]"

msgid "5400:状況がよく把握できなくて、思わず周囲をキョロキョロと見回してしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:I started looking around the room, unsure of what had just happened.[%p]"

msgid "5500:隣には背中を丸めたおばあさんが座っていた。目が皺に埋もれていて、寝ているのか起きているのかよく分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "5500:There was an old, hunched-up woman sitting next to me. Her eyes were buried so deep in her wrinkles that I couldn't tell if she was awake or not.[%p]"

msgid "5600:受付カウンターの上にある時計を見てみると、このロビーで待ち始めて１時間ほどが過ぎていた。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:I looked up at the clock above the reception counter and saw that I'd been here in the lobby for over an hour.[%p]"

msgid "5700:……もしかして、今のは夢？[%p]"
msgstr "5700:Was that just a dream?[%p]"

msgid "5800:昨日から寝てないから、待っているうちにうたた寝しちゃってたのか。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:Had I fallen asleep while I was waiting since I hadn't slept at all last night?[%p]"

msgid "5900:今の夢が現実だったらどんなによかっただろう。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:If only it had been real.[%p]"

msgid "6000:すごくガッカリだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "6000:I felt so disappointed.[%p]"

msgid "6100:結局、その後もさらに２時間ほど待たされて、ようやく名前を呼ばれた。[%p]"
msgstr "6100:In the end, I waited another two hours before they finally called my name.[%p]"

msgid "6200:診察室に入ると、さっき見た夢と同じことが繰り返されているかのような錯覚を覚える。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:When I went into the exam room, it was the same as I'd seen in my dream. I thought for a minute I was back in the dream again.[%p]"

msgid "6300:高科先生だって夢に出てきたのとほとんど同じだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:Dr. Takashina looked just like he had in my dream, too.[%p]"

msgid "6400:いや、最後に会った４年前とまるで変わってないだけか。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:Maybe he just hadn't changed much over the past four years.[%p]"

msgid "6500:でも先生はイスから立ち上がらなかったし、僕に握手も求めなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:But he didn't stand up, and didn't ask to shake my hand.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]高科[line]「今日はどうしました？」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]高科[line]What brings you here today?[%p]"

msgid "6700:そして夢のときのように、僕との再会を懐かしんだりもしなかったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6700:And he didn't seem happy to see me again, like in my dream.[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]拓巳[line]「え、あ、あの、西條、です」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]拓巳[line]Um, I'm, uh... Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]高科[line]「うん？\u3000ああ、これはご丁寧に」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]高科[line]Hmm? Oh, nice to meet you.[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]高科[line]「高科です。初めまして」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]高科[line]My name is Dr. Takashina. Let's get started.[%p]"

msgid "7100:診察室にはすぐに呼ばれた。もっと待たされるかと思ったけど、全然そんなことはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:It wasn't long at all before I was called into the exam room. I thought I'd be asked to wait longer, but that wasn't the case at all.[%p]"

msgid "7200:ロビーにいたたくさんの人たちはいったいなんだったんだろう。案外、サクラだったりするのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "7200:What about all those people in the lobby? Maybe they were all fakes, put there by the hospital to make it look busy.[%p]"

msgid "7300:４年前とは違う診察室だった。入っていくと、懐かしい顔が僕を出迎えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "7300:It was a different exam room than the one I'd been seen in four years ago, but I recognized how he welcomed me when I came in.[%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]高科[line]「やあ、西條くん」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]高科[line]Hello, Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "7500:高科先生は僕ににこやかな笑みを向けてくれた。[linebreak]４年前となにも変わっていない。そのことに安心した僕は、思いの丈をぶちまけていた。[%p]"
msgstr "7500:Dr. Takashina was looking at me with a cheerful smile. Nothing had changed since I'd last come here four years ago. Feeling relieved, I just let loose with everything I was feeling.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]拓巳[line]「せ、せ、先生、たす、助けて……」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]拓巳[line]D-Doctor... Help me...[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]高科[line]「ど、どうしたんだい？」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]高科[line]W-What's wrong?[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]拓巳[line]「変な……お、女が……僕にストーカー行為を……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]拓巳[line]T-There's this girl... She's stalking me.[%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]拓巳[line]「このままじゃ、が、学校にも、い、行けないし、い、家にも、い、一度、来られてて、場所知られてるから、あ、安心、できないし……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]拓巳[line]I can't go to school anymore... and she came to my house once and knows where I live... so I d-don't feel safe.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]高科[line]「……落ち着いて」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]高科[line]Calm down.[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]拓巳[line]「お、落ち着いてなんて、いら、いられないよっ」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]拓巳[line]I-I can't stay calm.[%p]"

msgid "8200:[name]拓巳[line]「あの、女、異常だ……っ。僕は、せ、正常なんだっ。それに、優愛だけじゃない、あ、悪魔女だって……」[%p]"
msgstr "8200:[name]拓巳[line]T-That woman is crazy. I'm n-normal. And it's not just Yua... It's that demon girl, too.[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]拓巳[line]「そうだ、悪魔女が、し、真犯人なんだっ」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]拓巳[line]That's right. The demon girl is behind the killings![%p]"

msgid "8400:[name]高科[line]「真犯人？」[%p]"
msgstr "8400:[name]高科[line]The killings?[%p]"

msgid "8500:[name]拓巳[line]「ニ、ニュージェネの……犯人だよっ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "8500:[name]拓巳[line]She's the NewGen killer![%p]"

msgid "8600:[name]拓巳[line]「ま、間違いないんだっ！\u3000僕は、じ、事件現場で、死体を、は、張り付けにしてる最中の、あの女を、み、見たんだっ」[%p]"
msgstr "8600:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'm sure of it. I-I saw her staking a corpse... to the wall.[%p]"

msgid "8700:[name]高科[line]「大丈夫だ、なにも心配いらないから」[%p]"
msgstr "8700:[name]高科[line]Everything's fine. You don't need to worry about a thing.[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]高科[line]「とにかく落ち着こう。いいね？」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]高科[line]Just calm down. All right?[%p]"

msgid "8900:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "8900:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "9000:諭されて、僕は口を閉ざした。[linebreak]いったいなにが大丈夫なのかはよく分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:I fell silent. I didn't understand what was fine.[%p]"

msgid "9100:でもプロの医者が、それも高科先生がそう言ってくれるんだから、きっとホントに大丈夫なんだ。そう自分に言い聞かせた。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:But if a professional, a doctor, especially Doctor Takashina, said so, I must be fine. That's what I told myself.[%p]"

msgid "9200:興奮したせいか、息が苦しい。僕は息を整える。[%p]"
msgstr "9200:I was getting so excited that I was having trouble breathing. I took a moment to catch my breath.[%p]"

msgid "9300:先生はそんな僕の様子をじっと見つめていた。[linebreak]やけに深刻そうだけど……[%p]"
msgstr "9300:He was staring at me with a grave look on his face. He seemed really serious.[%p]"

msgid "9400:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あの……ほ、ホントに、大丈夫……なの？」[%p]"
msgstr "9400:[name]拓巳[line]Um... am I really okay?[%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]高科[line]「もちろんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]高科[line]Of course.[%p]"

msgid "9600:[name]拓巳[line]「あんな、あ、危ない、女が……僕を、ね、狙ってるのに……」[%p]"
msgstr "9600:[name]拓巳[line]T-That... dangerous girl is... after me.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]拓巳[line]「なんで、そ、そう、言い切れるの……？」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]拓巳[line]How can you be so sure?[%p]"

msgid "9800:[name]高科[line]「理由を知りたいかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "9800:[name]高科[line]You want to know why?[%p]"

msgid "9900:僕がうなずくと、先生は小さく肩をすくめた。[linebreak]手に握ったペンを、無意識なのかしきりに指の上で回転させている。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:I nodded, and he sighed a little. He was fiddling a little with the pen in his hands as he spoke.[%p]"

msgid "10000:[name]高科[line]「なぜなら、君の言っている女の人は――」[%p]"
msgstr "10000:[name]高科[line]Because the girl you're talking about...[%p]"

msgid "10100:[name]高科[line]「この世には存在しないからだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "10100:[name]高科[line]She doesn't exist.[%p]"

msgid "10200:[name]拓巳[line]「……は？\u3000で、でも……」[%p]"
msgstr "10200:[name]拓巳[line]Huh? But... But...[%p]"

msgid "10300:[name]高科[line]「君は自分の妄想に怯えているだけなんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "10300:[name]高科[line]You're afraid of your own delusions.[%p]"

msgid "10400:その声音は、不気味なくらいに優しい。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:His voice was eerily kind.[%p]"

msgid "10500:僕は身を震わせる。止まらない。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:My body was shaking. It wouldn't stop.[%p]"

msgid "10600:どうしてだろう。[linebreak]先生はこんなに優しいのに……[%p]"
msgstr "10600:Why? He was being so kind.[%p]"

msgid "10700:[name]高科[line]「西條くん、君はその女の人には会っていない。分かるね？」[%p]"
msgstr "10700:[name]高科[line]Nishijo, you never met that girl. Do you understand?[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]拓巳[line]「わ、分からないよ……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]拓巳[line]I-I don't.[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]高科[line]「じゃあ、もっと具体的に言おうか」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]高科[line]Let me be more specific, then.[%p]"

msgid "11000:[name]高科[line]「君は、その女の人には会えるはずがないんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "11000:[name]高科[line]You can't have met her.[%p]"

msgid "11100:[name]高科[line]「もう７年間も、君は」[%p]"
msgstr "11100:[name]高科[line]Because for the past seven years,[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]高科[line]「この病院から」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]高科[line]you have not...[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]高科[line]「一歩も」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]高科[line]taken a step…[%p]"

msgid "11400:[name]高科[line]「外に」[%p]"
msgstr "11400:[name]高科[line]outside…[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]高科[line]「出ていないんだからね」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]高科[line]this hospital.[%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "11700:どういう……こと……？[linebreak]え？\u3000え？\u3000先生は、いったいなにを……[%p]"
msgstr "11700:What did he mean? Huh? Huh? What was he saying?[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]高科[line]「君はこの病院の精神科に、７年間入院している。そのことは分かるだろう？」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]高科[line]You've been in the psych ward of this hospital for the past seven years. You know that, right?[%p]"

msgid "11900:分からない……分かるわけがない。[linebreak]なんでこの人は、微笑みを浮かべながらこんなデタラメなことを言い出すんだ……[%p]"
msgstr "11900:I don't understand... I can't understand. Why was he telling me this crazy stuff with a smile on his face?[%p]"

msgid "12000:ふと自分が着ている服を見た。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:I looked down at the clothes I was wearing.[%p]"

msgid "12100:今日はブラチューの星来Ｔシャツの上に、デニムの長袖シャツを羽織って、下は一着しか持っていないジーパンっていう服装でこの病院に来たはずだった。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:When I'd come here, I was wearing a Seira t-shirt, and a long-sleeved denim shirt over it. I was wearing my only pair of jeans, too.[%p]"

msgid "12200:なのに、なぜか、[%p]"
msgstr "12200:So why...[%p]"

msgid "12300:今、僕が着ているのは、[%p]"
msgstr "12300:was I now wearing...[%p]"

msgid "12400:病院着だ。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:a hospital gown?[%p]"

msgid "12500:淡い黄緑色をしていて、ワンピースみたいになっている服。[linebreak]前を合わせて紐で結ぶだけの簡素なもの。下はズボンもはいていない。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:It was a pale green one-piece gown. A simple one that tied in the front with a string. I wasn't wearing pants beneath it.[%p]"

msgid "12600:僕は、いつ、着替えたんだっけ？[%p]"
msgstr "12600:When had I changed clothes?[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]高科[line]「ここは閉鎖病棟だから、お見舞いの人も来ない」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]高科[line]This is a closed ward. No visitors.[%p]"

msgid "12800:[name]高科[line]「入院患者さんも男女で別フロアに分けられていて、行き来はできない」[%p]"
msgstr "12800:[name]高科[line]And the patients are separated into male and female floors, which are locked off from each other.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]高科[line]「精神科の看護師は全員、男だし」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]高科[line]All the nurses in the psych ward are male.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]高科[line]「君の病室は完全に個室。窓もない」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]高科[line]And you don't have any roommates. Or windows, either.[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]高科[line]「つまり、君は７年間、女性と接触したことがないんだ。君の家族も含めてね」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]高科[line]You haven't had contact with a girl for the past seven years, including family members.[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]高科[line]「思い出したかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]高科[line]Do you remember now?[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……あああ……」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]拓巳[line]Aah... aah...[%p]"

msgid "13400:嘘だ……。[linebreak]そんなの嘘だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:No... It wasn't true.[%p]"

msgid "13500:僕は、入院なんてしてない。僕は渋谷でひとり暮らしをしてるし、エンスーではかなり名の知れた上級プレイヤーで、学校だって最低登校シフト表に従って週に２、３回だけどちゃんと行ってるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:I wasn't locked in some hospital room. I lived alone in Shibuya. I was a top-ranked player in ESO. I even went to school two or three times a week.[%p]"

msgid "13600:それにさっき、病院の受付の看護師さんとも事務的に話をした。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:And I'd talked to the nurse at the front desk just a minute ago.[%p]"

msgid "13700:“初診ですか？”“はいそうです”“ではこの用紙に必要事項を記入してお待ちください”[%p]"
msgstr "13700:“Is this your first time here?” “Yes.” “Then please fill out this form.”[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「嘘に決まってる……」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]It has to be a lie.[%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]高科[line]「……本当にそう思うのかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]高科[line]Do you really think so?[%p]"

msgid "14000:先生が、カルテになにかを書き込みながらつぶやく。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:He wrote something on my chart as he whispered.[%p]"

msgid "14100:なにを書いているのか僕には読めない。[linebreak]日本語じゃなかった。英語？\u3000いや、ドイツ語？[%p]"
msgstr "14100:I couldn't read what he was writing. It wasn't Japanese. English? No, German?[%p]"

msgid "14200:[name]高科[line]「だとしたら、君の精神はまだ異常だっていうことだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14200:[name]高科[line]If you do think that, it means you're still having mental problems.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]高科[line]「もうしばらくは入院が必要だね」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]高科[line]You'll have to stay in the hospital a while longer.[%p]"

msgid "14400:チラリと、先生が僕を一瞥する。[linebreak]憐れみの色をたたえた瞳。[linebreak]そんな目をされるなんて、以前は一度もなかったのに。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:He glanced at me. His eyes were filled with pity. He'd never looked at me like that before.[%p]"

msgid "14500:僕は力なくその場に膝を突いた。[linebreak]涙が溢れてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:I fell to my knees, helpless. The tears came quickly.[%p]"

msgid "14600:ああ、そうか。そうだったんだ。[linebreak]これまでの記憶は全部、僕の妄想だったんだ。[linebreak]異常なのは僕。頭がおかしいのは僕。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Oh, now I see. That's right. All of my memories were just delusions of mine. I was the abnormal one. I was the crazy one.[%p]"

msgid "14700:なんてひどいオチなんだ。[linebreak]でもまあ、もうどうでもいいや。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:What an awful ending. But, well... it didn't even matter now.[%p]"

msgid "14800:妄想だったとしても、惜しい記憶じゃないし。[linebreak]どうせまた新しく創り出せるんだろう？[%p]"
msgstr "14800:Even if the memories were just a delusion, they weren't particularly good ones, anyway. And I could just create new ones, right?[%p]"

msgid "14900:今度は、怖い事件が起きない世界がいいな。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Maybe I could have a world where nothing scary happened.[%p]"

msgid "15000:僕は社交的な性格で成績も優秀。女子にモテモテなんだ。グラビアアイドル並みの美人ばかりが僕の友達にいて、しかもみんながみんな僕のことが好きなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:I could be social and outgoing and get good grades. Girls would love me. All my friends would be girls who looked good enough to be models, and they'd all be in love with me.[%p]"

msgid "15100:そこで僕が、一つ屋根の下でみんなで暮らそうって提案するんだ。[linebreak]そして、楽しくて甘酸っぱくてちょっとドタバタな毎日が始まるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:And then I could suggest that we live under the same roof. That would be the beginning of fun, bittersweet, and slightly crazy days for me.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]拓巳[line]「ふひ……ふひひひ……」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]拓巳[line]Fweheheh.[%p]"

msgid "15300:無理に笑おうとした。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:I forced myself to laugh.[%p]"

msgid "15400:顔が、引きつった。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:It didn't really work. My expression froze up.[%p]"

msgid "15500:死にたくなった――[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I wanted to die.[%p]"

msgid "15600:ハッと我に返ると、僕はいまだにロビーのソファに座っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:Suddenly, I realized I was still sitting on the sofa in the lobby.[%p]"

msgid "15700:全身にイヤな汗をじっとりとかいている。ゾクリと背筋を悪寒が走った。[%p]"
msgstr "15700:My body was soaked with a terrible sweat. A cold chill ran down my spine.[%p]"

msgid "15800:状況がよく把握できなくて、思わず周囲をキョロキョロと見回してしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:I started looking around the room, unsure of what had just happened.[%p]"

msgid "15900:隣には背中を丸めたおばあさんが座っていた。目が皺に埋もれていて、寝ているのか起きているのかよく分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:There was an old, hunched-up woman sitting next to me. Her eyes were buried so deep in her wrinkles that I couldn't tell if she was awake or not.[%p]"

msgid "16000:受付カウンターの上にある時計を見てみると、このロビーで待ち始めて１時間ほどが過ぎていた。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:I looked up at the clock above the reception counter and saw that I'd been here in the lobby for over an hour.[%p]"

msgid "16100:……もしかして、今のは夢？[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Was that just a dream?[%p]"

msgid "16200:昨日から寝てないから、待っているうちにうたた寝しちゃってたのか？[%p]"
msgstr "16200:Had I fallen asleep while I was waiting, since I hadn't slept at all last night?[%p]"

msgid "16300:僕は深々とため息をついた。[linebreak]イヤな夢だった。夢……だよな……？[%p]"
msgstr "16300:I sighed, deeply. What an awful dream. It was a dream, right?[%p]"

msgid "16400:昨日までのことを思い出してみる。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:I tried to remember my life until yesterday.[%p]"

msgid "16500:大丈夫だ。記憶は連続している。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:It was okay. My memories were all connected.[%p]"

msgid "16600:僕は事件現場で悪魔女と遭遇し、優愛に騙され脅された。[linebreak]そして、自分が正常だって証明したくてこの病院に来た。そうだ、大丈夫。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I'd encountered the demon girl at the crime scene, and then Yua had lied to me and threatened me. And then I'd come to this hospital to prove I was sane. Yeah, it was all fine.[%p]"

msgid "16700:……実は妄想でしたっていうオチでも、よかったけど。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:I would've preferred if it was all a delusion, of course.[%p]"

msgid "16800:そして、また新しい妄想世界を創ってその中で楽しく過ごす方が、よっぽど幸せなのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:Maybe I would've been happier if I could've made a new world and had a lot of fun with it.[%p]"

msgid "16900:そう思えるくらい、今の状況は僕にとってうんざりするものだった。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I was just that sick of this world.[%p]"

msgid "17000:結局、その後もさらに２時間ほど待たされて、ようやく名前を呼ばれた。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:In the end, I waited another two hours before they finally called my name.[%p]"

msgid "17100:診察室に入ると、さっき見た夢と同じことが繰り返されているかのような錯覚を覚える。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:When I went into the exam room, it was the same as I'd seen in my dream. I thought for a minute I was back in the dream again.[%p]"

msgid "17200:高科先生だって夢に出てきたのとほとんど同じだ。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:Dr. Takashina looked just like he had in my dream, too.[%p]"

msgid "17300:いや、最後に会った４年前とまるで変わってないだけか。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:Maybe he just hadn't changed much over the past four years.[%p]"

msgid "17400:[name]高科[line]「今日はどうしました？」[%p]"
msgstr "17400:[name]高科[line]What brings you here today?[%p]"

msgid "17500:先生は“その記憶は君の妄想だ”なんて言い出したりはしなかった。[linebreak]だけど――[%p]"
msgstr "17500:He didn't start by telling me that all my memories were delusions. But...[%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]拓巳[line]「え、あ、あの、西條、です」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]拓巳[line]Um, I'm, uh... Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]高科[line]「うん？\u3000ああ、これはご丁寧に」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]高科[line]Hmm? Oh, nice to meet you.[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]高科[line]「高科です。初めまして」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]高科[line]My name is Takashina. Let's get started.[%p]"

msgid "17900:３時間も待たされて、ようやく名前を呼ばれた。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I waited another three hours before they finally called my name.[%p]"

msgid "18000:４年前とは違う診察室だったけど、入っていくと懐かしい顔が僕を出迎えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:It was a different exam room than the one I'd been seen in four years ago, but I was welcomed by a face I recognized.[%p]"

msgid "18100:この先生は、“誠実そうなおじさん”っていう形容がぴったり来る。老け顔だけど表情は柔らかいし、なによりもしゃべり方や態度にその要素がにじみ出ている。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:He was the very image of a “trustworthy older man.” He looked older than he probably was, but he had a kind expression, and that kindness came across in his mannerisms and way of talking.[%p]"

msgid "18200:最後に会った４年前とそれはちっとも変わってない。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:He hadn't changed at all in the four years since I'd last seen him.[%p]"

msgid "18300:この人は歳を取らないんだろうかと思っちゃいそうになるくらいだ。もともと年齢不詳だけど。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:I wondered if he'd even aged at all, not that I was even sure how old he was.[%p]"

msgid "18400:すがるような想いが僕の心の中でますます強くなった。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:The desire to beg him for help grew stronger and stronger within me.[%p]"

msgid "18500:この人なら頼りになる。この人なら僕を救ってくれる。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:He was somebody I could count on. He was somebody who would save me.[%p]"

msgid "18600:先生と再会できたことが、すごく嬉しかった。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:I was so happy to see him again.[%p]"

msgid "18700:先生の、僕へ向けた第一声を聞くまでは――[%p]"
msgstr "18700:Until I heard the first thing he said...[%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]高科[line]「今日はどうしました？」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]高科[line]What brings you here today?[%p]"

msgid "18900:その声は確かに柔らかで、人を安心させる優しさに満ちている。でも、かつて僕がこの病院に通っていた頃のような、親しげな感じはなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:His voice was soft and gentle, and put you at ease. But there wasn't the sense of friendliness I'd seen when I came here before.[%p]"

msgid "19000:あくまでも仕事として僕に接しているような――[%p]"
msgstr "19000:It was like he was talking to me for the first time.[%p]"

msgid "19100:だから僕はたまらず、名前を告げていた。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:I couldn't handle it, so I decided to remind him.[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]拓巳[line]「え、あ、あの、西條、です」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]拓巳[line]Um, I'm, uh... Nishijo.[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]高科[line]「うん？\u3000ああ、これはご丁寧に」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]高科[line]Hmm? Oh, nice to meet you.[%p]"

msgid "19400:[name]高科[line]「高科です。初めまして」[%p]"
msgstr "19400:[name]高科[line]My name is Takashina. Let's get started.[%p]"

msgid "19500:にこやかに頭を下げられた。[linebreak]僕は……なにも言えなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:He bowed to me. I... couldn't say anything.[%p]"

msgid "19600:“初めまして”[%p]"
msgstr "19600:“Nice to meet you.”[%p]"

msgid "19700:先生は確かに今、そう言った。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:That's what he had just said.[%p]"

msgid "19800:僕のこと……忘れてるんだ。[linebreak]それもそうだよな、もう４年だもんね……。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:He'd... forgotten me. It made sense. It had been four years, after all.[%p]"

msgid "19900:でも先生なら……先生ならきっと僕のことを覚えていてくれてるって思ってた。[%p]"
msgstr "19900:But I'd thought that he... he of all people would remember me.[%p]"

msgid "20000:そんな期待を、勝手に抱いてた。[%p]"
msgstr "20000:I'd kind of had that hope, whether it was fair or not.[%p]"

msgid "20100:だからそれを打ち砕かれたことで、僕の心の中に寂しさや虚しさが一気に溢れ出した。[linebreak]自分っていう存在が否定されたような気分だ。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:When that hope was shattered, it just made me sadder. It felt like I didn't matter.[%p]"

msgid "20200:先生は僕の目を見て語りかけてくる。[linebreak]僕はそれから目をそらした。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:He looked in my eye as he spoke, but I looked away.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]高科[line]「夢遊病かどうか調べてほしいと書いてあるが」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]高科[line]You said you want to find out if you were sleepwalking?[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]高科[line]「なにかあったのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]高科[line]Did something happen?[%p]"

msgid "20500:そう、確かにアンケート用紙にはそう書いた。[linebreak]でももう無意味だ。先生が僕のこと覚えてないんじゃ……[%p]"
msgstr "20500:That's right. That's what I'd said on the form. But it didn't matter now. If he didn't even remember me...[%p]"

msgid "20600:[name]星来[line]「別にいいじゃん」[%p]"
msgstr "20600:[name]星来[line]Who cares?[%p]"

msgid "20700:[name]星来[line]「先生が覚えてようが覚えてなかろうが、関係ないっしょ。[linebreak]最初の目的を忘れちゃダメ！」[%p]"
msgstr "20700:[name]星来[line]Who cares if the doctor remembers you or not? Don't forget why you came here![%p]"

msgid "20800:あ、そうか……。[%p]"
msgstr "20800:Oh, right.[%p]"

msgid "20900:僕は先生に会いに来たんじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "20900:I hadn't come here to see Dr. Takashina.[%p]"

msgid "21000:僕っていう人間は正常なんだって証明しに来たんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:I'd come to prove that I was normal.[%p]"

msgid "21100:先生との再会はあくまでおまけ。[linebreak]忘れられてるからなんだって言うんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Seeing him again was just a bonus. What did it matter if he forgot me?[%p]"

msgid "21200:星来たんが忠告してくれなかったら、[linebreak]危うく自分を見失っているところだったよ。ふう……。[%p]"
msgstr "21200:If Seira-tan hadn't reminded me, I might've broken down right there. Whew.[%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あの……」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]拓巳[line]Um...[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]拓巳[line]「……じ、自分でも知らないうちに、外に、出かけてて、[linebreak]パソコンで、ぶ、文章を打ってて、それをまったく、[linebreak]お、覚えてない、なんて……あり得ます、か……？」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]拓巳[line]I-Is it possible that you could say, leave your house, go to a computer, type a message... and then not... remember it at all?[%p]"

msgid "21500:[name]高科[line]「ほう」[%p]"
msgstr "21500:[name]高科[line]Oh?[%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]拓巳[line]「し、知り合いから……そう指摘されて[linebreak]……混乱、しちゃって……」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]拓巳[line]S-Somebody I know told me that I was doing that... And it really confused me.[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]高科[line]「その知り合いの人が冗談を言っているっていう可能性は、あると思うかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]高科[line]Do you think it's possible they were joking?[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "21900:優愛のあの目は、本気だった。[linebreak]僕をからかったりしているようには見えなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "21900:Yua's eyes had been dead serious. She didn't look like she was teasing me or anything.[%p]"

msgid "22000:少なくとも優愛は、優愛自身が語ったことを信じて疑っていなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "22000:If nothing else, she certainly seemed to believe what she was saying.[%p]"

msgid "22100:[name]拓巳[line]「分かり……ません……」[%p]"
msgstr "22100:[name]拓巳[line]I don't... know.[%p]"

msgid "22200:[name]高科[line]「なるほど」[%p]"
msgstr "22200:[name]高科[line]I see.[%p]"

msgid "22300:[name]高科[line]「ちなみに、その知り合いとはどういう関係だろう？\u3000恋人？」[%p]"
msgstr "22300:[name]高科[line]Can you tell me more about your relationship with this person? A girlfriend, perhaps?[%p]"

msgid "22400:[name]拓巳[line]「はあ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "22400:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "22500:なにをいきなり言い出すんだ、この人は。[linebreak]それとこれと、なにか関係があるのか？[%p]"
msgstr "22500:What was this guy talking about? What did that have to do with anything?[%p]"

msgid "22600:[name]高科[line]「いや、言い方が悪かったかな。じゃあ言い直そう」[%p]"
msgstr "22600:[name]高科[line]Hmm, that was probably not the right way to phrase it. Let me try again.[%p]"

msgid "22700:[name]高科[line]「その知り合いの人は、君が意識もないまま歩き回っているのを実際に目撃したのかな？」[%p]"
msgstr "22700:[name]高科[line]Did this person actually see you up and walking while you weren't awake?[%p]"

msgid "22800:なんだ、そういうことか。[linebreak]僕は首を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:Oh, was that what he meant? I shook my head.[%p]"

msgid "22900:[name]高科[line]「じゃあ、証拠はないわけだ」[%p]"
msgstr "22900:[name]高科[line]Then there's no evidence of it.[%p]"

msgid "23000:さらにもう一度、僕は首を振る。[%p]"
msgstr "23000:I shook my head again.[%p]"

msgid "23100:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そいつ……た、探偵気取り……で。[linebreak]いろいろ、証拠を突きつけてきて……」[%p]"
msgstr "23100:[name]拓巳[line]S-She thinks she's some kind of detective. She showed me all kinds of evidence.[%p]"

msgid "23200:[name]高科[line]「ふむ、そういうことか」[%p]"
msgstr "23200:[name]高科[line]Hmm. I see.[%p]"

msgid "23300:[name]高科[line]「ちなみにこれまでにも夢遊病の兆候はあったかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "23300:[name]高科[line]And has there been any evidence or history of sleepwalking in your past?[%p]"

msgid "23400:[name]拓巳[line]「い、いいえ……」[%p]"
msgstr "23400:[name]拓巳[line]N-No.[%p]"

msgid "23500:[name]高科[line]「朝目覚めたら、いつものベッドじゃなくて違う場所で寝てた、っていうことは過去に一度でもあった？」[%p]"
msgstr "23500:[name]高科[line]You've never woken up to find yourself not in your bed, anything like that?[%p]"

msgid "23600:[name]拓巳[line]「い、いいえ」[%p]"
msgstr "23600:[name]拓巳[line]N-No.[%p]"

msgid "23700:[name]高科[line]「じゃあ、その知り合いに言われたのが初めてっていうことだね？」[%p]"
msgstr "23700:[name]高科[line]Then you didn't notice anything until she told you?[%p]"

msgid "23800:僕は力なくうなずいてから、思い切って口を開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "23800:I nodded, weakly, before forcing myself to speak.[%p]"

msgid "23900:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕……ね、寝て、ない……んです……」[%p]"
msgstr "23900:[name]拓巳[line]I-I wasn't... sleeping.[%p]"

msgid "24000:[name]高科[line]「もしかして怖いのかな？\u3000でもそんなに深刻になる必要はないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "24000:[name]高科[line]Are you scared? You don't need to be so worried.[%p]"

msgid "24100:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、いや……その……」[%p]"
msgstr "24100:[name]拓巳[line]No, um... uh...[%p]"

msgid "24200:そうじゃなくて――[linebreak]僕が言いたいのはそういうことじゃなくて――[%p]"
msgstr "24200:That wasn't it. That wasn't what I wanted to say.[%p]"

msgid "24300:でもなんて説明すればいいのか、頭の中がうまく整理できず、まごまごしているうちに言い出すタイミングを失ってしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "24300:But I wasn't sure how to explain it, and couldn't get my thoughts together in my head. I lost my chance to speak.[%p]"

msgid "24400:先生はカルテになにやら走り書きをしてから、座っているイスを回転させて僕に背を向け、診察室の奥へと身を乗り出した。[%p]"
msgstr "24400:He scribbled something in his chart before spinning around to turn away from me, and then leaned forward, toward the back of the exam room.[%p]"

msgid "24500:[name]高科[line]「[ruby-base]葉月[ruby-text-start]はづき[ruby-text-end]くん、ちょっと」[%p]"
msgstr "24500:[name]高科[line]Hazuki, come here.[%p]"

msgid "24600:[name]葉月[line]「はい」[%p]"
msgstr "24600:[name]葉月[line]Yes, sir.[%p]"

msgid "24700:駆け寄ってきたのはまだ若い看護師で、先生がカルテを見せながら小声でなにやら指示すると、彼女はすぐに奥に引っ込んでいった。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:A young nurse came over. The doctor showed her my chart and said something softly to her, and then she quickly went back further into the room.[%p]"

msgid "24800:なんだろう……？[%p]"
msgstr "24800:What was that about?[%p]"

msgid "24900:戸惑っていると、先生はまた僕に向き直る。[linebreak]それから、優しい口調で夢遊病がどういうものかについて教えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "24900:He turned to face me again. Then, in a gentle tone, he explained to me what sleepwalking was.[%p]"

msgid "25000:人は眠りに落ちると、まずレム睡眠が始まり、やがてノンレム睡眠に移行する。[%p]"
msgstr "25000:When someone falls asleep, he said, first they enter REM sleep, and then non-REM sleep.[%p]"

msgid "25100:レム睡眠っていうのは、身体は休息状態だけど脳が覚醒に近い状態で活動している睡眠のこと。[%p]"
msgstr "25100:REM sleep was when the body was asleep, but the brain was close to fully awake.[%p]"

msgid "25200:それに対してノンレム睡眠は、脳の活動が休止状態になるより深い眠りのことを言う。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:Non-REM sleep was a deeper sleep, when the brain also rested.[%p]"

msgid "25300:[name]高科[line]「夢遊病は、ノンレム睡眠のときに起きやすいって言われてる」[%p]"
msgstr "25300:[name]高科[line]Sleepwalking is said to occur mostly during non-REM sleep.[%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]高科[line]「脳が通常の活動をしていないから、普通の受け答えとかは成立しにくいけど、ちゃんと返事もするし、階段などを踏み外さずに上り下りすることだってできる」[%p]"
msgstr "25400:[name]高科[line]The brain isn't as active as it normally is, so you can't really engage the person in conversation, but they're able to answer questions and even walk up and down stairs without missing a step.[%p]"

msgid "25500:[name]高科[line]「原因としては、精神的なストレスを抱えてるときになりやすいんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "25500:[name]高科[line]It happens often during periods of extreme psychological stress.[%p]"

msgid "25600:[name]高科[line]「子供に多い症状だけど、成人でもよくある症状なんだよ。これで分かっただろう？\u3000深刻になることはないって言った意味が」[%p]"
msgstr "25600:[name]高科[line]Sleepwalking is most common in children, but happens to adults as well. You understand now, right? It's not something you need to be so worried about.[%p]"

msgid "25700:[name]拓巳[line]「はあ……」[%p]"
msgstr "25700:[name]拓巳[line]I see.[%p]"

msgid "25800:でも……[%p]"
msgstr "25800:But...[%p]"

msgid "25900:僕は、寝てないんだ。寝ていないのに、自分で覚えていない行動を取っていたんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "25900:I wasn't sleeping. I wasn't sleeping, and yet I was still doing things I didn't remember.[%p]"

msgid "26000:ＲＯＯＭ３７で『将軍』がチャットに書き込んだとされる時間、僕はずっとエンスーをやっていたはずなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "26000:The whole time I'd been supposedly typing into that chat as Shogun in room 37, I'd thought I'd been playing ESO.[%p]"

msgid "26100:それって、夢遊病って言うのかな？[linebreak]教えてもらいたかったけど……先生はどんどん話を進めてしまっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "26100:Was that what you'd call sleepwalking? I wanted to ask, but the doctor just kept talking.[%p]"

msgid "26200:[name]高科[line]「夢遊病かどうかを調べる方法としては、いくつかある。一番手っ取り早いのは、ここのベッドで寝てもらうことだね。ははは」[%p]"
msgstr "26200:[name]高科[line]There are several ways to test for sleepwalking. The fastest would be to have you fall asleep in this bed right here. Hahaha...[%p]"

msgid "26300:[name]高科[line]「ただ、特定条件じゃないと発生しない場合もあるかもしれない。例えば自分のベッドじゃないとダメ、とか」[%p]"
msgstr "26300:[name]高科[line]But sometimes it only occurs under specific conditions, such as when you're sleeping in your own bed, for instance.[%p]"

msgid "26400:[name]高科[line]「意識がない状態で出歩くにしても、目的もなくフラフラと歩き続けるのか」[%p]"
msgstr "26400:[name]高科[line]Another question is whether, when you're walking about while unconscious, you just walk around randomly,[%p]"

msgid "26500:[name]高科[line]「それともなんらかの強迫観念があって、それに影響されてなんらかの“一連の目的”を持って出歩いているのか」[%p]"
msgstr "26500:[name]高科[line]or if some kind of obsessive-compulsiveness compels you to follow a certain series of actions.[%p]"

msgid "26600:[name]高科[line]「それに君の精神状態についても、特定の条件下じゃないとダメかもしれない。自宅のベッドの上ならリラックスできるけど、ここじゃリラックスのしようがないわけだ」[%p]"
msgstr "26600:[name]高科[line]It's also possible that your mind needs to be in a certain mental state. For example, you could feel relaxed at home, but not here.[%p]"

msgid "26700:[name]高科[line]「どうする？\u3000とりあえず寝ていってみるかい？」[%p]"
msgstr "26700:[name]高科[line]Well? Want to try taking a nap here?[%p]"

msgid "26800:調べてもらうことには損はないはず。[linebreak]夢遊病じゃないって証明できた後で、本来するつもりだった質問をしてみよう。[%p]"
msgstr "26800:It wouldn't hurt to try. I could make sure I wasn't sleepwalking, and then ask him the question I'd come to ask.[%p]"

msgid "26900:奥にある診療用ベッドまで、さっきの葉月とかいう看護師さんに案内された。[%p]"
msgstr "26900:The nurse, Hazuki, lead me to a bed in the back.[%p]"

msgid "27000:眠るためのものじゃないから、ベッドは硬くて寝心地が悪かった。[%p]"
msgstr "27000:It wasn't meant for sleeping, so it was hard and uncomfortable.[%p]"

msgid "27100:まあ、僕が普段寝ているソファに比べれば全然問題ないレベルだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "27100:Still, it was better than the sofa I was used to sleeping on.[%p]"

msgid "27200:[name]葉月[line]「３時間くらいしたら、起こしに来ますから」[%p]"
msgstr "27200:[name]葉月[line]I'll be back to wake you up in three hours.[%p]"

msgid "27300:この看護師さん、かわいいなあ……。[%p]"
msgstr "27300:This nurse was really cute.[%p]"

msgid "27400:ベッドに横たわったまま、視線を合わせないようにしつつその顔を盗み見る。[%p]"
msgstr "27400:I lay on the bed, glancing at her while trying to make sure our eyes didn't meet.[%p]"

msgid "27500:ちょっと童顔の顔立ちはなんだか頼りなさそうで、不幸オーラを醸し出している雰囲気だけど、仕事はテキパキとこなしている。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:She had a somewhat young, helpless-looking face, and the air of someone whose life wasn't really working out the way they wanted it to. Still, she went about her work quickly and steadily.[%p]"

msgid "27600:昔のエロゲに出てきそうなヒロインって感じ。しかも病院の陵辱もの。ふひひ。[%p]"
msgstr "27600:She felt like one of the girls from an old H-game. One set in a hospital, with lots of rape. Fweheheh.[%p]"

msgid "27700:[name]葉月[line]「できるだけ目は離さないようにしていますので、安心して眠ってくださいね」[%p]"
msgstr "27700:[name]葉月[line]I'll make sure to keep an eye on you as best I can, so don't worry about a thing. Just get some sleep.[%p]"

msgid "27800:つまり、僕に夢遊病の症状が出て勝手に徘徊し始めても、ちゃんと保護してくれるっていうことだ。[%p]"
msgstr "27800:In other words, she'd be watching to make sure I didn't get up and start walking around.[%p]"

msgid "27900:[name]葉月[line]「それでは、ごゆっくり」[%p]"
msgstr "27900:[name]葉月[line]Good night.[%p]"

msgid "28000:看護師さんはわずかに笑みを浮かべた後、カーテンを閉めて去っていった。[linebreak]真っ白いカーテンに囲まれて、僕は深く息を漏らす。[%p]"
msgstr "28000:She smiled a little before closing the curtains and leaving. Surrounded by the white curtains, I let out a deep breath.[%p]"

msgid "28100:周囲からは、先生が患者さんを診察している声や、他の看護師さんたちがパタパタと歩き回る音や、診察室のドアを開け閉めする音などが聞こえてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "28100:I could hear lots of things: the voice of the doctor as he examined his patients, the other nurses walking around, even the door as it opened and closed.[%p]"

msgid "28200:さすがに落ち着かないなあ。[linebreak]こんな状況で眠れるかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "28200:It was pretty hard to relax. Could I really sleep like this?[%p]"

msgid "28300:ダメもとで僕は目を閉じた。[%p]"
msgstr "28300:I tried to close my eyes, just to see if it would work.[%p]"

msgid "28400:どうしても脳裏には『将軍』からのグロ画像や、杭で張り付けにされたあの惨殺死体の映像が浮かびそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "28400:The second I did, the guro images that Shogun sent and the sight of the corpse nailed to the wall came flooding back to me.[%p]"

msgid "28500:なので無理矢理、星来たんの姿を思い浮かべた。[%p]"
msgstr "28500:I forced myself to think of Seira-tan instead.[%p]"

msgid "28600:[name]星来[line]「タッキー、外出嫌いなのに病院来るなんてすごい！」[%p]"
msgstr "28600:[name]星来[line]Wow, Takky! You hate going outside, but you still came to a hospital! Amazing![%p]"

msgid "28700:[name]星来[line]「あたし前から思ってたんだけどさ、タッキーって実はすごく強い男の子だよね」[%p]"
msgstr "28700:[name]星来[line]You know, I always thought you were a really strong boy.[%p]"

msgid "28800:僕の妄想の中で、星来が躍動する。星来がかわいい声でさえずってくれる。[%p]"
msgstr "28800:Inside my delusion, she was happily bouncing up and down. Next, she whispered to me in a sweet voice.[%p]"

msgid "28900:[name]星来[line]「あたし、そんなタッキーの強さが、ス・キ♪」[%p]"
msgstr "28900:[name]星来[line]I love how strong you are, Takky!♪[%p]"

msgid "29000:[name]星来[line]「それにタッキーは夢遊病なんかじゃないよ。あたし、毎日タッキーのこと見てるもん。だから分かるんさ」[%p]"
msgstr "29000:[name]星来[line]And you don't sleepwalk, by the way. I see you every day, so I know.[%p]"

msgid "29100:[name]星来[line]「三次元女になんか騙されちゃダメだゾ。タッキーにはあたしがいるっしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "29100:[name]星来[line]Don't let any 3D girls fool you. You've got me, right?[%p]"

msgid "29200:[name]星来[line]「またあのコンテナハウスで、２人きりで過ごそうね、ぼけなす♪」[%p]"
msgstr "29200:[name]星来[line]Let's go back to your container house and spend our days together, just the two of us, dork.[%p]"

msgid "29300:ふひひ。[linebreak]星来たんかわいいよ星来たん。[%p]"
msgstr "29300:Fweheheh. Seira, you're so cute. Seira...[%p]"

msgid "29400:やっぱり星来たんは僕の理想の嫁。[linebreak]星来たん以上の女はいない。[%p]"
msgstr "29400:Seira was my ideal wife, after all. No girl could ever be better than her.[%p]"

msgid "29500:三次元？\u3000なにそれ？[%p]"
msgstr "29500:3D? Who cares about 3D?[%p]"

msgid "29600:ああ、早く帰りたい。[linebreak]帰って星来たんに“おかえり”って笑顔で出迎えられたい。[%p]"
msgstr "29600:I couldn't wait to go home. Seira would be waiting for me with a big smile and a “Welcome home!”[%p]"

msgid "29700:待っててね星来たん。すぐ帰るから――[%p]"
msgstr "29700:Just wait, Seira-tan. I'll be coming for you.[%p]"

